attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the first pair of sidebars, and he then screws them on, and then assembles the second pair of sidebars and screws them on, assembles the base frame and inserts the base frame with the sidebars. He assembles the bottom tray and screws it with the bracket to the sidebar, assembles the middle and top tray, screws them with their bracket to the sidebar, and finally screws the wheels on.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the black tubes.

attributes.Transcription: Start by putting together the tubes

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the black base frame.

attributes.Transcription: Assure the first tubes with the long sides together.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student took the wrong tube to assemble the base frame.

attributes.Transcription: You may have to go other.
Button the next to each other about the open ends in the middle and looking upwards.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the first sidebar with the base frame.
The student assembles the bottom grid tray.

attributes.Transcription: Take the biggest of the trays and put at the bottom of what you just built.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should make sure to use one of the black brackets on the outside.

attributes.Transcription: Make sure to use one of the black brackets on the outside.

attributes.Action sentence: The student places the black grid tray between the side bars.

attributes.Transcription: Make sure to take the second biggest tray and put it at the bottom first.
And attach the smallest tray at the bottom.
Make sure the first one isn't smaller than the second piece.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The first and the second smallest tray should be at the bottom.

attributes.Transcription: The first and the second smallest tray should be at the bottom otherwise "*unintelligible*".

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the middle tray.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should insert by turning the bolt to the top round please, not the whole wheel, just the circular thing at the top.

attributes.Transcription: Insert by turning the bolt to the top round, not the whole wheel, just the circular thing at the top.
You can stop the record now.
